text: Hawkeye is an American TV miniseries that is part of the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU). Featuring the Marvel Comics characters Clint Barton / Hawkeye and Kate Bishop / Hawkeye, the series was created by Jonathan Igla and was on Disney+ from November 24 to December 22, 2021. It is the fifth MCU TV series to be produced by Marvel Studios. Jeremy Renner and Hailee Steinfeld star as Clint Barton and Kate Bishop.
